Read Time out when getPullRequests list if there are more than 140 pages of PullRequests in a repo;

I want to grab a huge amount of pullrequests so I wonder whether there is a way to provide a method to allow me to set how many pages of pullrequest I want to get, so that I can get them in in batches.

thx very much.

